710143f-b.title: Manhattan: 8th Avenue - 30th Street (West)
710143f-b.text:
Eighth Ave., north from West 30th Street, showing in a
set of two views one of the main arterial thoroughfares of
Manhattan and beneath whose street bed runs the Jndependent
Eighth Ave. Subway, a Municipal venture. On the left is the
general Post Office occupying the westerly front of the Avenue
between 31st and 33rd Streets. The large light manufacturing
building aeen,is at the N.W. corner of 33rd Street.
March 21, 1938.
